net.sourceforge.waters.model.compiler
Class ModuleCompiler

java.lang.Object
  net.sourceforge.waters.model.compiler.ModuleCompiler
public class ModuleCompiler
extends Object

The main module compiler class.

A module compiler takes Waters modules (ModuleProxy) as input and translates them into a product DES structures (ProductDESProxy). It evaluates all parameterised and loop structures and loads and instantiates other modules as needed.

Robi Malik
